&lt;p&gt;Whodun-WHAT? First I thought it&amp;apos;s referring to the site. In &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.pythonchallenge.com/about.php&#34;&gt;About Page of python challenge&lt;/a&gt; I found the site was written by Nadav Samet. Not correct.&lt;/p&gt;
